unittitle_ssm: Mark Solomon and Robert Kaufman Research Files on African Americans and Communism
abstract_ssm: The collection is comprised of research materials regarding African Americans and communism accumulated by two scholars: Mark Solomon and Robert Kaufman. It contains clippings, articles, printed ephemera, internal documents, published documents (principally from radical organizations), research notes, and government surveillance documents.
corpname_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives
subject_ssm: African American labor union members --  History
Labor unions and communism -- United States.
title_ssm: The Cry Was Unity: Communists and African Americans, 1917-1936
